  "3273070": {
    "name": "Re:SSS",
    "steam_appid": 3273070,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/deece42b56ad60d579f06ebacc1413ac.poster.avif?t=1762847211\" width=800 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/deece42b56ad60d579f06ebacc1413ac.webm?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/deece42b56ad60d579f06ebacc1413ac.mp4?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >集齐六颗，就能实现任何愿望的[龙珠]。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将成为会说话的蛇[蛇男]，击败敌人并利用从敌人那里夺取的技能卡，打造更强大的卡组。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成你的旅程，利用最强的卡组实现愿望，揭开世界的秘密！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/86d0e5a55b694ad2ed04cfbf34bce7f9.avif?t=1762847211\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>1. </strong>用攻击卡攻击敌人！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/797db53ba57fcf64c58b3de55e6f621f.poster.avif?t=1762847211\" width=800 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/797db53ba57fcf64c58b3de55e6f621f.webm?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/797db53ba57fcf64c58b3de55e6f621f.mp4?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >攻击卡是直接对敌人造成伤害的卡片。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通常分为攻击单个敌人的[单体攻击]、一次性造成多次伤害的[连续攻击]和同时攻击多个敌人的[范围攻击]。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >根据卡片的属性，可以造成[物理 / 魔法 / 复合]伤害。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﻿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >﻿<strong>2. </strong>使用支援卡来增强战略！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/d747566c1b6211da0e7d62f530794e02.poster.avif?t=1762847211\" width=800 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/d747566c1b6211da0e7d62f530794e02.webm?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/d747566c1b6211da0e7d62f530794e02.mp4?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过支援卡，你可以使用多种辅助战斗的效果。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >不仅可以使用简单的战斗辅助效果，如增益/减益/恢复，还可以进行更具战略性的操作，如搜索所需的卡片或制约敌人的行动。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﻿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >﻿<strong>3. </strong>使用反击卡来制约敌人的行动！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/7568214d312a8035acc44dade94e71ba.poster.avif?t=1762847211\" width=800 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/7568214d312a8035acc44dade94e71ba.webm?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/7568214d312a8035acc44dade94e71ba.mp4?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >反击卡是在对方回合中[与敌人的特定行动链式]触发的卡片。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通常可以通过干扰敌人的行动或获得巨大优势的效果，更有效地破解敌人的战略。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﻿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >﻿<strong>4. </strong>使用强力效果的消灭卡吧！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/2463a74e112a789dd3b651c7693eb057.poster.avif?t=1762847211\" width=800 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/2463a74e112a789dd3b651c7693eb057.webm?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/2463a74e112a789dd3b651c7693eb057.mp4?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﻿消灭卡是使用后直接消失，无法回收，但具有更强大效果的卡片。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >它本身非常强大，但也有一个优点，那就是利用其使用后消失的特性，可以压缩卡组，更容易将所需技能加入手牌中。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﻿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >﻿<strong>5. </strong>使用触发和被动效果来拓宽战略的范围！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/dd0aa19ce3692a4004191987f3cb11f0.poster.avif?t=1762847211\" width=800 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/dd0aa19ce3692a4004191987f3cb11f0.webm?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/dd0aa19ce3692a4004191987f3cb11f0.mp4?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某些卡片具有触发效果，当它们送往手牌/卡组/墓地时可以发动，或者，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >也有持续触发的被动效果选项，当卡片处于卡组/手牌/墓地等特定位置时会持续触发。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过这些特殊效果，考虑卡片之间的协同作用，增强你的战略吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﻿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >﻿<strong>6. </strong>通过组合多张卡片，创造出拥有最强效果的联合卡吧！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/c609eb2a7ccdbd5aa8331b77d6345c8e.poster.avif?t=1762847211\" width=800 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/c609eb2a7ccdbd5aa8331b77d6345c8e.webm?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/c609eb2a7ccdbd5aa8331b77d6345c8e.mp4?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﻿在战斗中，通过组合手牌中的多张卡片，可以合成拥有强大效果的联合卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好素材，合成最强的卡片，击败敌人吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/ccd41857ee05a809e1ace880856aa700.avif?t=1762847211\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >﻿<strong>1. </strong>通过获得经验，提升属性并获得强力的特性！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/e86fe6af688752baf1dace435d92e3ab.poster.avif?t=1762847211\" width=800 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/e86fe6af688752baf1dace435d92e3ab.webm?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/e86fe6af688752baf1dace435d92e3ab.mp4?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﻿击败敌人提升等级，获得属性和特性点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用获得的属性点来强化角色，并使用特性点解锁特殊能力吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﻿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >﻿<strong>2. </strong>使用物品和遗物来增强你的战略！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/9e2c38e079505959ca5313d93907b4c0.poster.avif?t=1762847211\" width=800 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/9e2c38e079505959ca5313d93907b4c0.webm?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/9e2c38e079505959ca5313d93907b4c0.mp4?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﻿在商店购买的[物品]和击败敌人后获得的[遗物]，可以装备到快捷栏中，辅助战斗并扩大战略的范围！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/2d6ae2f9e931580bf41f97417e64e699.avif?t=1762847211\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >﻿<strong>1. </strong>分析敌人的特点，制定战略并攻略敌人的模式！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/3be4bfb8fac8c651b5a7cc87c59a669b.poster.avif?t=1762847211\" width=800 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/3be4bfb8fac8c651b5a7cc87c59a669b.webm?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/3be4bfb8fac8c651b5a7cc87c59a669b.mp4?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个敌人都有独特的特性和卡片。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >分析敌人的信息，制定战略并攻略敌人的模式！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﻿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >﻿<strong>2. </strong>在冒险世界中击败敌人，完成实现愿望的旅程！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/09e7ff7329c4488e504a53b7bca258b8.poster.avif?t=1762847211\" width=800 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/09e7ff7329c4488e504a53b7bca258b8.webm?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/09e7ff7329c4488e504a53b7bca258b8.mp4?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >蛇小子是谁，过去发生了什么事情？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败挡在前方的敌人，推动故事发展，听听令人兴奋的蛇小子的冒险故事吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﻿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >﻿<strong>3. </strong>在训练场上享受与亲手制造的敌人进行卡片对战吧！<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/38662f8905a32f0cd186a55135bd7b8c.poster.avif?t=1762847211\" width=800 height=476 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/38662f8905a32f0cd186a55135bd7b8c.webm?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/38662f8905a32f0cd186a55135bd7b8c.mp4?t=1762847211\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在训练场上，你可以自定义击败的敌人的[属性]和[卡组]。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >打造最强的敌人，享受超越极限的卡片对战吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >﻿</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3273070/extras/c473924a4bd01f92e78efb5cd4d6e3c7.avif?t=1762847211\" width=600 height=120 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
